Chart below looks at returns on buying NFTs via Blur bids and flipping, one of the main farmer strategies.

A few takeaways:
1) Season 3 so far has been pretty positive for farmers

2) A LOT of ETH was lost in Season 2 but that was heavily concentrated in the first few months (think Gitcoin, OSF/Mando dumping 72 apes etc.)

3) Farmers got a lot more sophisticated as time went on and started losing much less, especially by September

4) Season 3 is turning a bit more negative after a strong start.

5) With the large airdrops received, farming became a much more profitable strategy after the first few months of S2.
